@EestiGirl1 as soon as I find the person for it. I'll let you know & fill you in on what they're like. Curiosity is good, shows intellect :)

@EestiGirl1 ooh gross!! How does that even work?! But as genetic wonders go that takes some topping! :-)
@EestiGirl1 self interest. When you start to get famous you'll find me badgering to be your agent! Not so. I like encouraging creativity ;-)

@EestiGirl1 you're welcome. I don't know any other genetic wonders so it's a treat for me too ;-)

@EestiGirl1 still a moment to be cherished. First glimpse of fame & fortune! Who knows where it will lead?! :-)

@EestiGirl1 lol. I can be wise every now & then. Just not often! Nitey nite :-))

@EestiGirl1 yeah we do! Lol. Sleep well ;-))
@EestiGirl1 that's the get out of all people who snore ;-))
@EestiGirl1 lol. I'll plead guilty for butt soreness it's ok! Been great chatting. Nite ;-))

@EestiGirl1 the hitting the bed or the snoring?! Snoring is definitely an event! :-))
@EestiGirl1 no wonder. It's late & I'm keeping you up.You go get some sleep before you end up dropping off in the chair :-)

@EestiGirl1 yeah. Sort of an Eco friendly superhero! Definitely the future for crime fighting. I do like green too. Very restful :-))

@EestiGirl1 that's true. Life is unfair! Just can't let it drag you down, fight on pickle girl! Beat life at its own game :-))
